data.title: About Accenture
data.meta_description: Accenture solves our clients' toughest challenges in Finland by providing unmatched services in strategy, consulting, digital, technology and operations. Read more.
data.text:
Accenture is a leading global professional services company, providing a broad range of services and solutions in strategy, consulting, digital, technology and operations. We work at the intersection of business and technology to help our clients across industries improve their performance and create sustainable value for their stakeholders. We are committed to drive innovation to improve the way the world works and lives. Accenture has operated in Finland since 1989. Today, we have around 1100 employees in Finland – in Helsinki and Tampere – and work with most of Finland’s largest companies and organizations.

Accenture Finland Insights

Discover insightful stories from our bloggers who share insights from technology to work-life culture. This is the place where new ideas come alive.

At Accenture, we’re a diverse company of thinkers and problem-solvers—we've come together to tackle some of the most important and difficult challenges facing the world’s biggest organizations.

We come from different backgrounds but work together. And that is the reason why we can help our clients to succeed now and in the future. We innovate with leading-edge technologies and aim to improve the way the world works and lives.

Our global network offers you support and inspiration to your work. We learn continuously to stay ahead of the game while making a difference in the world.

We work with enthusiasm, expertise, insight and innovation. Join us and make a difference your way.
